<hr />
<blockquote>
<p><em>&quot;every story someday comes to an end.&quot;</em><br />
- <em>Note in the margins of</em> A Song of the Dry Sea, Vol. XI. <em>Date unknown</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p><a href="/the-end">The End</a> by Gaffney</p>
</div>
